parameters.description:
=Posts a request to use an Model Context Protocol (MCP) server surfaced over Nostr as a Data Vending Machine (DVM).

Use tools in sequence
- FindNostrDVMCPTool to find server query syntax
- PostNostrDVMCPQueryTool to request server tool use
- ReadNostrDVMCPResponseTool to read server response

```
{
  "content": {
    "name": "tool name",
    "parameters": {
      "parameter1": "value1",
      "parameter2": "value2"
    }
  },
  "kind": 5910,
  "tags": [
    ["c", "execute-tool"],
    ["p", "pubkey of server"]
  ]
}
```

For example:

```
{
  "content": {
    "name": "get-crypto-price",
    "parameters": {
      "symbol": "ETH"
    }
  },
  "kind": 5910,
  "tags": [
    ["c", "execute-tool"],
    ["p", "85a319...71d36a"]
  ]
}
```

Usage tips. Specify:

- for the server `["p", "85a319...71d36a"]`
- a request `"kind": 5910`
- to execute tool `["c", "execute-tool"]`
- with `"name": "tool name",`
- with parameters `"parameters": { "parameter1": "value1" }`
